Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.96,0:43:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,best you can with what you have, yes? To do the best as you can. It's nice
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.94,0:43:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to see yourself as unworthy and not worth the effort. The future looks bleak.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.17,0:43:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm incapable and passive rather than active, reject help and accept help. People
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.46,0:43:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,reject help all the time. People go over the edge with people offering their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.61,0:43:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,because they don't want to take it, because they're getting too much payoff from the
