Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.61,0:43:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Filthy, dirty, homeless, abject, poverty-stricken. You're like an affront to divinity, see? You
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.78,0:43:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,lay there in the doorway, yeah. An aversion then to getting over it and moving on and
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.65,0:44:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore it is really a subtle form of resistance, subtle form of resistance. Okay, move on.
