Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.88,0:45:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,happiness is within. So grief then saw the source of happiness. You are my happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.00,0:45:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to put you in a bad place later.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.94,0:45:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You contribute and support my happiness, that's a good place, but you are the source, you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.00,0:45:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,are it, then if I lose you, I've lost it all and go into grief and so go back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.44,0:45:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The attraction of this also is the emotionality of it. See the source of happiness is in here
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.59,0:45:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of out there, you know? Okay, so we'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.19,0:45:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is full of solutions. As we said, life moves actually from perfection to perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.75,0:45:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't move from imperfection to perfection or from incomplete to complete. It moves from
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.73,0:46:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,complete to complete. At every moment, it's perfect. Perfectly despondent. You're perfectly
