Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.78,0:46:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,flower. Now it's a perfect unfolded flower. Now it's a perfect half unfolded flower. Now
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.07,0:46:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a perfect drooping flower. Now it's a perfect withered flower. Now it's a perfect
