Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.40,0:46:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,as it actualizes. Everything is perfect and then perfect and then perfect. So, if you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.80,0:46:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,want to improve the world, you're going to have to go from perfect to more perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.48,0:46:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.48,0:47:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a downside in the tragedies of the world that tend to energize the ambition to
