Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.86,0:47:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of the danger, dramatizing it, the emotionalism. And, of course, fear has to do with being
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.05,0:47:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,on the front of the crest of the wave. And just like grief is clinging to the past, fear
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.96,0:47:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is anticipating.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.96,0:47:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Equanimity and peace is to be right on the peak of the wave without resisting this or
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.57,0:47:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,without clinging to that. With neither clinging nor resisting. Neither attraction nor aversion.
