Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.30,0:49:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When you wann' go up and want to carry you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.42,0:49:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,know.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.42,0:49:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get on board the boat, everyone wants to wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.42,0:49:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When you want to let me do the follow-up,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.78,0:49:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.78,0:49:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.78,0:49:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's part of what's good about Sierra. You know what's not right. You do! .
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.78,0:49:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,they prayed. That was interesting. The other thing that was interesting is an occasional
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.21,0:49:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,one will tell you, maybe about once a year, a survivor of a tornado will tell you how
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.01,0:49:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,they were lifted up 50, 100 feet in the air, and they went into a state of sublime peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.55,0:50:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A number of them did that. I was whirled up into the air 100 feet over, and then suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.53,0:50:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,a great profound sense of peace came upon me. If all else fails, get sucked up in a
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.46,0:50:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,tornado. It's a poor time to emotionalize, right? You're 100 feet whirling in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.57,0:50:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Another time you can blubber later, but right now. All right, so we'll let go of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.94,0:50:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll let go of fear, then, and perhaps see it as the indulgence of the child within
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.59,0:50:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,us.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.19,0:50:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.96,0:50:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,When is fear appropriate? I don't know when it's fear. Caution is a different thing. Caution
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.11,0:50:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is not the same thing. Caution is thinking, anticipating, but it's not emotionalizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.30,0:51:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear is going into hysteria and coming apart, see? And you can't come apart if the situation
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.44,0:51:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of real danger, where you need to stay cool. You have to learn to handle it calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.44,0:51:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, in the end, you can surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.26,0:51:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You can
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.69,0:51:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.90,0:51:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.46,0:51:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.01,0:51:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.34,0:51:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. H complimenting a lot today, and thank you to Dr. David.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.61,0:51:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. David.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.82,0:51:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.21,0:51:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So big deal, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.46,0:51:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So even facing death, you see, fearful emotionalization is not even necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.07,0:51:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,because with acceptance, you transcend into serenity.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.90,0:51:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And he got it from me, and I got it from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.94,0:51:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I got it from the near-death experience where I realized that fear was not,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.57,0:52:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,it wasn't really a near-death experience, but what people think is that death is not a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.13,0:52:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, on a certain level, everybody sort of knows that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.63,0:52:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,because when we calibrated a near-death experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.44,0:52:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it shows a major jump in consciousness before and after the experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.59,0:52:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas out-of-body experience, you don't see any change at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.61,0:52:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A person who calibrates at 340 goes out of body for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.11,0:52:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,comes back in body, later they still calibrate at 340.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.28,0:52:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A person near death calibrates at 340, they come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.69,0:52:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,they can maybe calibrate, you know, 560 or 570 or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.65,0:52:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And we asked, why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.42,0:52:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And we got because out-of-body is really experiencing that you're a spirit and not a body,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.53,0:52:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and you know that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.65,0:52:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already spent eons as a spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.57,0:52:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore, you haven't learned anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.40,0:52:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew that all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.28,0:53:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you get out of the body, you're back where it's more familiar than being in the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.26,0:53:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Being in the body is really actually strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.36,0:53:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Being out of the body is more familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.76,0:53:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not a surprise you didn't learn anything new when you went out of body
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.51,0:53:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,because you knew that's who you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.03,0:53:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew that you were a spirit all along, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.03,0:53:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That you are in space wherever you think you are in space,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.03,0:53:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,wherever you think you are, you're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.11,0:53:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.19,0:53:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So we let go of fear then of death by total acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.19,0:53:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That death is not a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.19,0:53:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And we surrender our life to God, trust God.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.19,0:53:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it's time to blow up, so you blow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.19,0:53:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.86,0:53:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,More fear, oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.21,0:53:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the attraction is fears tend to proliferate.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.21,0:53:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, you let go of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.21,0:53:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We like to harbor our fears and justify them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.21,0:53:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We like to reject the cause as being out there, out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.21,0:53:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The cause of the fear is out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.21,0:53:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The cause of the fear is the Komodo dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.21,0:54:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the commander, he's the one that's causing my fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.25,0:54:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, projecting the source as external.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.38,0:54:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, fear sees life as strictly physical, focuses on the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.92,0:54:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And the bottom fear of the ego is really death.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.92,0:54:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And surrendering a stack of fears, if you use the technique of it, then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.88,0:54:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you take a fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.88,0:54:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to lose my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.88,0:54:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.88,0:54:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then I won't have transportation.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.88,0:54:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.88,0:54:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll lose my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.88,0:54:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.88,0:54:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll have to walk to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.88,0:54:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.88,0:54:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But there aren't any jobs like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.88,0:54:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then you won't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.88,0:54:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.88,0:54:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.88,0:54:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll be poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.88,0:54:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so you're poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.88,0:54:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.88,0:54:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll starve to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.88,0:54:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.88,0:54:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, at the bottom of every stack of fears is death.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.94,0:54:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Physical death.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.94,0:54:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Physical death.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.94,0:54:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you say, so what to physical death, nothing scares you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.94,0:54:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing really frightens you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.94,0:54:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the basic fear, once you surrender completely to the physical death, the whole
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.94,0:55:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,stack is brought down.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.94,0:55:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember in Estes they used to talk about stacks, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.94,0:55:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, fear is a big stack.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.94,0:55:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the bottom of that stack is the fear of physical death.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.94,0:55:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, once you've accepted physical death, then most of the fears that we have, which are
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.94,0:55:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,focused on the body and loss of possessions and things, disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.23,0:55:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.23,0:55:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You do that by acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.57,0:55:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the one that really bothers most people most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.57,0:55:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, fears come along and grief comes along, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.57,0:55:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,People are apathetic about certain things in their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.57,0:55:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But the desire and wantingness is the one that really bothers the most people most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.57,0:55:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the attraction of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.57,0:55:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Money, gain, control, getting, winning the election, approval, success, fame, acquisitions,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.84,0:55:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,conquest, of course, being right.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.84,0:56:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Being right, people are willing to die right and left for being right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.67,0:56:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They would rather die and be right than not be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.67,0:56:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego doesn't mind dumping your body at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.69,0:56:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than admit defeat, the ego will walk you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.69,0:56:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.65,0:56:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,People die for illusions all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.65,0:56:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In my lifetime, 100 million people, probably twice that, have died chasing some illusion rather than admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.65,0:56:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Chairman Mayo's economic agricultural plan resulted in the starvation of 30 million people.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.71,0:56:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayo's Little Red Book.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.17,0:56:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The faith in Chairman Mayo, God bless him.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.32,0:56:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Resulted in the death of 30 million people by starvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.65,0:56:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The greatest famine in all of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.48,0:56:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, would you think Marxism maybe is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.48,0:57:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.48,0:57:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We will spread it further into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.48,0:57:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The inability to learn, the pride of the ego then.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.25,0:57:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the desire to be right, to control, approval, all these things we are very familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.25,0:57:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's part of everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.25,0:57:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We all fear appearing passive, weak, a failure, poverty, losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.34,0:57:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And many people want to be noticed at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.59,0:57:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the extremes to which people go to be noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.59,0:57:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Say anything, no matter how outrageous, as long as you're on camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.59,0:57:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Or get on the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.59,0:57:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we'll go next.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.59,0:57:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The dualities of anger is closer a little bit to the animal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.34,0:57:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you feel expanded and stirred up, bigger than life with anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.34,0:58:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It gives you a feeling to dramatize and emotionalize and to be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.36,0:58:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the animal in you growls and shows its teeth and tries to win by intimidation.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.13,0:58:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The last thing it wants is to be calm, be at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.13,0:58:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Afraid it will appear weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.13,0:58:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't want to give in, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.13,0:58:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, not wanting to see a bad guy go free.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.30,0:58:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.30,0:58:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha said you don't have to worry about getting even with your enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.30,0:58:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they will bring themselves down by their own hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.30,0:58:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They will bring themselves down by their own hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.30,0:58:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And with consciousness calibration, of course, we affirm the truth of that over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.30,0:58:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's move to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.30,0:58:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.71,0:58:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the next one?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.67,0:58:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it is the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.17,0:58:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder I can't find the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.17,0:59:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.07,0:59:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about spiritual pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.07,0:59:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not talking about self-esteem.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.94,0:59:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-esteem is earned.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.94,0:59:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it's not ego-inflating.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.94,0:59:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Pride is something, a projection that we impose.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.94,0:59:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And it gives you status.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.94,0:59:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And it gets you noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.94,0:59:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And you get to be superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.94,0:59:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to be an insider.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.94,0:59:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to be elite.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.94,0:59:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.94,0:59:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Politically elite or politically correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.94,0:59:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to be above the common people.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.94,0:59:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is, of course, the paradox of egalitarianism.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.23,0:59:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is that all people are of equal value.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.23,0:59:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But some people are more valuable than others.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.23,0:59:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning us mainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.23,0:59:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason is because we're more egalitarian than anybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.28,0:59:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And that makes us superior to the rest of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.28,1:00:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So the downside of which is humility.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.11,1:00:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear you may look down on.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.11,1:00:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You may just be ignored because you're common and ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.11,1:00:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst of all things, of course, is to be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.11,1:00:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And people would rather die than be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.11,1:00:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They do it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.15,1:00:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see a whole other generation of people dying rather than admitting that they were following a false teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.36,1:00:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,An error.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.36,1:00:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.36,1:00:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.71,1:00:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.53,1:00:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If what we're witnessing is creation unfolding, you know, evolution is creation unfolding,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.48,1:01:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,then what we view as mistakes really represent a success because they demonstrate the outcome of a fallacy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.63,1:01:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If 30 million people starve to death according to a certain belief system,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.67,1:01:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the automatic demonstration of falsity.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.90,1:01:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So we see that falsity then, instead of trying to prevent its occurrence in the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.00,1:01:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,we try to counter it, but it serves its own purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.00,1:01:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So completely surrendering the world to gods sees it as not wanting to change the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.00,1:01:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but instead to become aware of its ultimate purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.00,1:01:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the ultimate opportunity for karmic,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.76,1:01:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,for karmic evolution,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.76,1:01:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to undo negative karma and gain positive karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.76,1:01:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If this were a heavenly realm and everybody calibrated at 600,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.30,1:01:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,there would be no purpose to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.30,1:01:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you can't predict the future,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.48,1:02:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,your future.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.63,1:02:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The future is, is not possibly set,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.51,1:02:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,can't possibly be set,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.51,1:02:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,because it hasn't been created yet,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.51,1:02:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,because we all contribute to the evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.51,1:02:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of the expression of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.51,1:02:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we haven't done so yet,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.51,1:02:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't possibly predict the future,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.51,1:02:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,because it as yet has no reality,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.51,1:02:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it's only a potentiality,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.51,1:02:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,has no reality,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.51,1:02:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can't predict the future,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.76,1:02:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because it has no reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.76,1:02:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could predict the future,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.86,1:02:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that would confirm predestination,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.86,1:02:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that everything that is bound to happen
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.86,1:02:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is already predestined.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.07,1:02:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If predestination were the rule,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.07,1:02:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,our lives would be of no value.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.07,1:02:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be like omatons,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.07,1:02:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,just fulfilling a role
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.07,1:02:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,like something in a movie, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.07,1:02:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Reciting a script.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.07,1:02:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd all be following a script.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.32,1:03:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There would be no karmic gain.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.09,1:03:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So the anticipated pleasures here,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.09,1:03:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of course, we're very familiar with control
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.09,1:03:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and familiarity,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.09,1:03:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the excuses of not wanting to
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.09,1:03:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,or can't kind of try,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.09,1:03:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the fears of surrendering,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.09,1:03:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,moving to the unknown,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.09,1:03:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth of...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.23,1:03:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So we already said,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.23,1:03:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,with a gun at your head,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.23,1:03:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the I can't reveals itself
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.23,1:03:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,as a truth that I won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.23,1:03:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.36,1:03:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,With a gun at your head, you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.36,1:03:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can't is not the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.36,1:03:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I want is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.36,1:03:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So anytime you think you can't do something,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.36,1:03:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,remind yourself you mean you won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.36,1:03:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually it's too much effort,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.36,1:03:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and bother.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.36,1:03:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, that's why you can't
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.36,1:03:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,clean up the garage.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.36,1:03:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't that you can't,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.36,1:03:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it's that you don't want to,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.36,1:03:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,because it lacks sufficient pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.36,1:04:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so we'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.36,1:04:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.63,1:04:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.17,1:04:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.17,1:04:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So we did the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.17,1:04:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to spend the rest of the afternoon
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.17,1:04:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,feeling guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.17,1:04:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Slide 32.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.88,1:04:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.15,1:04:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Slide 32, boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.19,1:04:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Socrates.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.36,1:04:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.88,1:04:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.01,1:04:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have a different way now
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.01,1:04:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of understanding kinesiology,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.05,1:04:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that it is clinical,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.05,1:04:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,not academic.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.05,1:04:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Academic means set in stone.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.05,1:04:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Clinical means variable.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.05,1:04:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's considered a healthy
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.05,1:04:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,physical measurement
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.05,1:04:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is a sign at one point
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.05,1:04:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in the evolution of medicine,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.05,1:04:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,a decade later is not.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.05,1:05:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's constantly evolving
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.05,1:05:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and learning.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.05,1:05:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And today, just a matter of an hour ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.05,1:05:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we learned the demonstration
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.05,1:05:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Heisenberg principle
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.05,1:05:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that all of us looking at
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.05,1:05:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,favorably in a loving way
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.05,1:05:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,all that exists
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.05,1:05:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,are already uplifting all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.17,1:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Uplifting all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.17,1:05:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.59,1:05:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us doing that,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.59,1:05:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,doing that,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.59,1:05:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,affect the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.59,1:05:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of all mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.59,1:05:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This group here,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.07,1:05:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,sizeably,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.07,1:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,affects the overall consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.07,1:05:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,level of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.42,1:05:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.42,1:05:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,By virtue of the awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.42,1:05:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,of levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.61,1:05:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is indicative of truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.61,1:05:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a very powerful group.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.61,1:05:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a very powerful group.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.09,1:05:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have like respect for
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.63,1:06:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that which has been given
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.63,1:06:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you have respect for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.76,1:06:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.76,1:06:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the respect takes the form
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.76,1:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,out of thankfulness and gratitude
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.76,1:06:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to use it
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.76,1:06:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,for the good of all mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.76,1:06:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do to raise
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.88,1:06:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.88,1:06:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of all of mankind?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.88,1:06:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We just stumbled upon it, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.88,1:06:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because loving
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.88,1:06:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to see the worth and the value
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.88,1:06:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and the sacredness
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.88,1:06:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of all that exists
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.88,1:06:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is the process of sanctification.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.88,1:06:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.88,1:06:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.88,1:06:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So thereby,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.76,1:06:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the self sanctifies creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.76,1:06:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thereby,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.76,1:06:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,does creation become sanctified
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.76,1:06:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,by our experience
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.76,1:06:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and witnessing of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.76,1:06:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.76,1:06:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a value to all of us
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.76,1:06:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,collectively as well as individually
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.76,1:06:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that somehow we serve
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.76,1:06:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the evolution of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.76,1:06:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a very rare group.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.76,1:07:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Statistically,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.76,1:07:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the chances are like
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.76,1:07:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,one in ten zillion.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.76,1:07:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But a group like this
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.92,1:07:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,we just confirmed
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.92,1:07:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is profoundly important
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.92,1:07:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to the evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.36,1:07:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of humanity
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.40,1:07:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and the evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.40,1:07:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of the level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.59,1:07:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The evolution of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.59,1:07:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is already on the upswing
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.59,1:07:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and a group like this
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.59,1:07:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that kick starts it
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.59,1:07:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,through the momentum.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.40,1:07:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.44,1:07:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so what happens
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.44,1:07:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,when you find something like that
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.44,1:07:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is you revere the gift,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.44,1:07:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you revere it,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.55,1:07:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see it as a gift.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.55,1:07:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, thank you, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.55,1:07:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of gratitude
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.55,1:07:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dumbfounded
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.55,1:08:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,with the revelation
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.19,1:08:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of the responsibility
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.19,1:08:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and the power and the gift
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.19,1:08:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring a greater lovingness
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.19,1:08:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to this experiential world.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.19,1:08:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, O Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.19,1:08:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we do collectively
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.19,1:08:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,give thanks for ourselves
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.19,1:08:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and for our lives
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.19,1:08:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and for our inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.19,1:08:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All of those who agree,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.19,1:08:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,say amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.19,1:08:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.19,1:08:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, isn't that neat?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.19,1:08:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That was some lunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.19,1:08:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go to that restaurant again.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.19,1:08:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That was on a fish sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.19,1:08:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.96,1:08:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But those awarenesses
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.35,1:08:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,come out of nothingness,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.35,1:08:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.35,1:08:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Not out of thinkingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.35,1:08:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.35,1:08:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say you discuss a subject,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.35,1:08:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you forget all about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.35,1:08:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Two or three hours later, wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.56,1:08:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly the inference of that
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.56,1:08:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,settles upon you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.67,1:09:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I told you
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.89,1:09:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,early in life,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.89,1:09:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a religionist,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.89,1:09:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,very devout.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.21,1:09:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,One day walking through the woods,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.31,1:09:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the totality of the suffering
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.31,1:09:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of all of mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.31,1:09:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of history
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.31,1:09:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,unfolded itself
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.76,1:09:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,through conscious awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.19,1:09:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't thinking about it,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.19,1:09:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing. Walking through the woods
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.19,1:09:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,in a beautiful day
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.35,1:09:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and out of nowhere
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.42,1:09:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the totality of the suffering
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.42,1:09:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,of all of mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.42,1:09:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout all of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.15,1:09:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It was staggering.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.60,1:09:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that moment
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.60,1:09:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I became an atheist.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.71,1:09:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,With the same dedication
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.71,1:09:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and devotion I was
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.71,1:09:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,a devout atheist.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.71,1:09:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't a half-you-know-what
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.71,1:09:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,atheist, I was a devoted one.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.81,1:10:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I went from atheist to agnostic,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.81,1:10:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,which is much better.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.81,1:10:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Atheism is also egotism.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.81,1:10:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's saying you know
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.81,1:10:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is no God,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.81,1:10:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,which is idiotic.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.81,1:10:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The agnostic is an honest.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.81,1:10:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The agnostic says,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.81,1:10:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I of my own self
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.81,1:10:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,am unable to prove
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.81,1:10:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,nor disprove the existence of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.81,1:10:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That is honesty.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.81,1:10:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,On a calibrated level
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.81,1:10:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,agnostic
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.81,1:10:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,does not calibrate negative
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.81,1:10:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're being honest.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.81,1:10:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.81,1:10:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In and of your own limited ego
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.81,1:10:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you really cannot say that God
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.81,1:10:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,either exists or does not exist.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.81,1:10:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a different paradigm
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.81,1:10:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and a different dimension.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.81,1:10:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way for the human mind
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.81,1:10:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,which stops at 499
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.81,1:10:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to be able to affirm the reality
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.81,1:10:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and the existence of that
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.81,1:10:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's an honest statement.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.81,1:10:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're doubtful,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.59,1:10:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,forget being an atheist
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.59,1:11:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and cling to being agnostic
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.59,1:11:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,because that is devotion to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.18,1:11:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The devotion to the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.18,1:11:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,persisted.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.18,1:11:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,First it was
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.18,1:11:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,vested in
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.18,1:11:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,religion, religiosity.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.18,1:11:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it was invested in
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.18,1:11:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,for a moment
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.40,1:11:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,atheism
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.47,1:11:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but then quickly shifted
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.47,1:11:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to agnosticism.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.47,1:11:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But at all times
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.47,1:11:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the dedication was to the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.47,1:11:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and throughout psychoanalysis
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.47,1:11:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,all the years every day on the couch
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.47,1:11:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Freudian and then Jungian
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.47,1:11:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and various others
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.47,1:11:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the dedication was to search for
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.47,1:11:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and reach the absolute
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.47,1:11:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,core of truth itself
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.47,1:11:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and the mind
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.47,1:11:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,just refused
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.47,1:11:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,all possible answers
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.47,1:11:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and saw that they were belief systems
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.47,1:11:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but the core of that which I am
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.47,1:11:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that which I am
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.92,1:11:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,drilled right through
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.85,1:11:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and had to reach the very
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.85,1:12:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,essence and the source of truth itself
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.85,1:12:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of truth in life and existence
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.85,1:12:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and that took me
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.85,1:12:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,as I've related before
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.85,1:12:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to the depths of hell
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.85,1:12:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the depths of hell are far worse than
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.85,1:12:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,no one can imagine
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.94,1:12:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.94,1:12:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it's beyond conceptualizing of the human mind
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.94,1:12:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's non-linear
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.94,1:12:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,depictions of hell are all linear
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.17,1:12:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience is non-linear
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.17,1:12:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,timeless
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.17,1:12:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and eternal
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.97,1:12:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,eternal darkness forever
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.97,1:12:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,with no hope ever of salvation
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.97,1:12:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,goes on for eons
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.97,1:12:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,eons
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.71,1:12:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,eons of abandon all hope
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.71,1:12:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,ye who enter here
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.06,1:12:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and out of the silence of that
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.06,1:12:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,non-linear
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.06,1:12:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,hopelessness beyond all hope
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.06,1:12:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a voice arose within
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.06,1:12:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and said
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.69,1:12:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,if there is a god I ask him for help
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.69,1:12:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and then oblivion
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.69,1:12:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and then
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.69,1:13:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly the lights turned on again
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.69,1:13:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,all of existence shone forth
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.31,1:13:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,as the glory of god as
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.39,1:13:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,all of creation
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.35,1:13:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you see a validation
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.35,1:13:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of your own worth no matter who or what you are
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.35,1:13:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,what you do
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.75,1:13:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,by your sheer presence
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.75,1:13:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you see that your mere witnessing
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.75,1:13:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the lovability and the sacredness
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.75,1:13:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,of all of creation is already changing
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.75,1:13:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,creation
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.75,1:13:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,this group here is changing
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.28,1:13:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,in which creation is unfolding
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.60,1:13:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,wow
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.64,1:13:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you see that doesn't appeal to the ego at all
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.64,1:13:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that's sort of scary in a way
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.64,1:13:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because you get wow
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.00,1:13:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,we have been somehow given this
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.00,1:13:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,possibility
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.02,1:13:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the pen is
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.06,1:13:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,mightier than the sword
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.06,1:13:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you see to know to really know this
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.06,1:13:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is already transforming potentiality
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.06,1:14:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that a group
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.18,1:14:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,knows that it has somewhat of
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.18,1:14:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,some kind of an input
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.18,1:14:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,destiny
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.18,1:14:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and destiny of mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.18,1:14:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,alright let's see if that's so
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.18,1:14:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,we have permission to ask that
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.56,1:14:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of this group
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.56,1:14:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that this group does play a part in the ultimate
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.56,1:14:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,destiny of the evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.56,1:14:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,of man on this planet
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.56,1:14:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,part of creation
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.56,1:14:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,a critical part of creation
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.56,1:14:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,a critical part of evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.56,1:14:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,ok so in as much as you play a
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.60,1:14:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,critical part in evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.60,1:14:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,creation has
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.17,1:14:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,unfolding of evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.32,1:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,via consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.31,1:14:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,which is it's field
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.31,1:14:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,a group such as this
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.31,1:14:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is changing the destiny
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.31,1:14:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,of mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.18,1:14:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,let's see if that's so
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.92,1:14:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,resist
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.72,1:14:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so mealy mouthing won't help you
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.72,1:15:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,anymore
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.52,1:15:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,what can I do just poor me
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.52,1:15:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a clerk at the grocery store
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.52,1:15:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,alright
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.68,1:15:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so you own
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.68,1:15:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to move you closer to
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.73,1:15:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the realization of the self
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.73,1:15:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,for the capital S is the source of your own existence
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.73,1:15:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,because if you accept this
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.73,1:15:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,about yourself you move closer
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.73,1:15:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to the truth of the source of your own existence
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.73,1:15:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you diminish this
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.73,1:15:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the voice of the
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.73,1:15:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,ego you diminish the voice of the
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.73,1:15:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,self and you've opened
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.73,1:15:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the door for the expression of the
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.73,1:15:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,self for the capital S
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.73,1:15:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and out of this meditation today
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.73,1:15:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,some people here are going to be
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.73,1:15:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,realizing the full
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.73,1:15:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,presence of the self
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.93,1:15:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so help me
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.93,1:15:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,alright so we'll take a break
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.06,1:15:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we're going to do questions and answers
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.06,1:15:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to spend more time with that
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.06,1:15:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,more in the future it's more informal
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.06,1:15:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not didactic
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.07,1:15:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,we've supplied all the didactic
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.07,1:16:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,material you need
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.07,1:16:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and we've armed
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.14,1:16:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you with the defense if you're accused of being
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.14,1:16:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual that you're
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.14,1:16:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,applying the Heisenberg principle to all
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.14,1:16:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of life's expressions
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.14,1:16:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll meet you after the break which is
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.14,1:16:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,what three
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.14,1:16:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,what
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.13,1:16:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,no I wanted to
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.52,1:16:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,stop earlier because I wanted to give more time for
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.52,1:16:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,questions and answers
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.63,1:16:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll take maybe 20 minutes
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.63,1:16:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to leave more time for
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.63,1:16:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,interchange
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.63,1:16:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and more of the traditional
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.63,1:16:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,teacher role
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.63,1:16:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,with the group where we
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.63,1:16:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,exchange with each other back and forth and
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.63,1:16:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,discuss and express
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.63,1:16:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,in a non didactic non formal
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.63,1:16:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,way sometimes I feel
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.63,1:16:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,like I'm being too much like a college prof
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.63,1:16:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and you know presenting sort of a
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.63,1:16:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,linear didactic kind of a
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.63,1:16:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding but that's part of
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.63,1:16:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding to transcend the mind
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.63,1:16:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you first satisfy it with
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.63,1:17:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the information it wants to know
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.63,1:17:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and now that it's got that information
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.63,1:17:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it can transcend that information
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.63,1:17:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and evolve into its own
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.63,1:17:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,potentiality as a knowingness
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.63,1:17:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than a knowing about
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.63,1:17:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the knowingness
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.63,1:17:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,occurs as a consequence
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.63,1:17:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of becoming that
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.63,1:17:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so first you have to know what it is you want to
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.63,1:17:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,become then what's
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.63,1:17:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,preventing you you drop that
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.63,1:17:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and then your life becomes
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.63,1:17:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the expression of
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.63,1:17:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,prayer so
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.75,1:17:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,our hope is that through the lectures
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.75,1:17:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,your life becomes the
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.75,1:17:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,expression of your own potentiality
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.75,1:17:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that your life is your prayer
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.75,1:17:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,your life is the prayer
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.75,1:17:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,of who you are and the expression of who
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.75,1:17:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you are which as we can see
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.75,1:17:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,benefits all mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.93,1:17:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,amen so we'll see you after a break
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.93,1:18:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,take these with me
